    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the period from about 1920 to 1740 BCE in Anatolia. The period is characterized by contacts with Mesopotamia particularly through trade with Assyrian merchants who founded colonies such as the town of Kultepe in Anatolia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al período desde aproximadamente 1920 al 1740 a.C. en Anatolia. El período se caracteriza particularmente por los contactos con Mesopotamia por el comercio con mercaderes Asirios que fundaron colonias como el pueblo de Kultepe en Anatolia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de periode van circa 1920 tot 1740 v. Chr. in Anatolië. De periode kenmerkt zich door contacten met Mesopotamië die vooral verliepen via de handel met Assyrische kooplieden die kolonies stichtten zoals de stad Kultepe in Anatolië.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指自西元前1920年至西元前1740年間，於安納托力亞發展的時代。此時代特色為與美索不達米亞（Mesopotamia）間的往來交流，特別是透過與亞述商人間的貿易，後者並於安納托力亞各處建立了殖民城鎮，如灰山（Kultepe）鎮。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
